			<DIV></DIV>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
<P>Necromancers can't mez because there are Enchanters for that.</P>
<P>Fear was fun once. I kinda miss it.</P>
<P>Undead Nukes are the only thing I can see being upgraded. We shouldnt have to nuke 10 times to match 1 hit of a pallys sword.</P>
<P>Degeneration and Crippling Claud - "These spells were central to luclin group play and now have paled away."&nbsp; No these spells always sucked, I was there.</P>
<P>Our lifetaps are the best spells we have for resists. What really should be looked at is why on some mobs the only dots I can land are low level clicky dots from items I got before Jesus walked the earth. I can mem the exact same spells and they won't land. Are pants really that powerful?</P>
<P>Our dot trap is perhaps the prettiest and most useless spell ever created. Pls delete it.</P>
<P>&nbsp;</P>
<P>&nbsp;</P>
